ên Chẩn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-An-Th%E1%BA%A1ch/T%C6%B0-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Ph%C3%B9ng-Nguy%C3%AAn/poem-yYzmJYyfDenzDmn6zPp1gQ">Tư Vương Phùng Nguyên - 思王逢原</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-An-Th%E1%BA%A1ch/author-9cGSHCUvFAIW_3kTfbKANw">Vương An Thạch</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C4%83ng-Qu%E1%BB%91c-Phi%C3%AAn/%E1%BB%A8c-%C4%91%E1%BB%87/poem-ShqMOyHAaPzqXVv_NTktug">Ức đệ - 憶弟</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C4%83ng-Qu%E1%BB%91c-Phi%C3%AAn/author-nwGIjF6JjQC812vXoHUn9A">Tăng Quốc Phiên</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/V%E1%BB%8Dng-H%C3%A1n-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-li%E1%BB%85u-s%E1%BA%AFc-k%C3%BD-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-T%E1%BB%83/poem-40-2nrF_oL0kZSOVgPnaTQ">Vọng Hán Dương liễu sắc ký Vương Tể - 望漢陽柳色寄王宰</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/author-8WYDeeki5xZo8eD-k6Sk5A">Lý Bạch</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/Xu%C3%A2n-kh%C3%AA-hoa-%E1%BA%A3nh/poem-FQUmLCObSW5bHJTTdXh0yA">Xuân khê hoa ảnh - 春溪花影</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/author-JHbQVfC53E2lRJL-xE616A">Nguyễn Khuyến</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
